Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 算是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷同學要回家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要我幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不用啦 不用啦
