Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord0\1c&H383838&\frz38.76\pos(332,398)}所以小瑞妳的傘借我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以小瑞妳的傘借我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要把人家的傘拿走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,妳說夢話吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,香織！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺真是禍不單行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,香織那傢伙 還真的拿我的傘回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,內、內卷同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？ 伊萬莉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那個呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.00,BackGround,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那之後我馬上到這邊找伊萬莉同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.28,BackGround,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她在那！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 妳在做什麼 伊萬莉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這…是雨水？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,亦或是…淚水呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,「亞爾斯安戰記」第二章中 與摩利安娜訣別的那一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,答對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,…不是啦 妳會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不要小看我 內卷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我身上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有溫蒂妮的加護啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:38.30,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※溫蒂妮\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}四大元素精靈中的水精靈。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學妳也在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,的確是那兩人會做出的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那內卷同學為什麼還留在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是在等宇佐美同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不是把傘借給朋友了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,小瑞就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.54,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\1c&H49403F&\3c&HDCD7D3&\fs45\frz339.6\frx336\fry2\move(321,97,361,107,0,2497)}香\N織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,香織…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我一起撐傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝…呃！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\1c&H271F3F&\3c&HFAEEEC&\pos(292,202)\frz10.87}咳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\1c&H271F3F&\3c&HFAEEEC&\frz1.946\pos(394,158)}咳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{7\bord3\1c&H271F3F&\3c&HFAEEEC&\frz354.1\pos(496,182)}咳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\1c&H271F3F&\3c&HFAEEEC&\frz350.3\pos(574,186)}咳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\1c&H271F3F&\3c&HFAEEEC&\pos(314,348)\frz358.9}師\N傅\N!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 宇佐美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那個… 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那時他到底想說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在竊笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,早、早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是知道內幕的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我是絕對不會說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是指「她和內卷同學撐一把傘回去」的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼妳會知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要小看了新聞社的情報網
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,挺行的嘛 瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不 並不是妳們想的那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他還是沒有注意到妳的心意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不過也好 暫時保持這種距離也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,根據新聞社以往的統計
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟升上三年級也會退出社團
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要是身在不同班級 為了備考
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也會變得說不上話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不趁現在二年級的時候順利發展 戀情是不會有結果的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好有說服力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的例外是 假設兩人進了同一所高中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有可能嗎 內卷同學和小瑞考上同一所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 的確照這樣下去的話一定沒戲唱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再想也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要順其自然！ 順其自然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 升上三年級的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小瑞…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再想了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,替我想想啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.03,BackGround,,0,0,0,,哎 你是說宇佐美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我喜歡上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡上宇佐美了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟她很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,除了她的兔子髮飾很可愛之外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,生氣時會變得有點野蠻這點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,裙底不時會走光這點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看來你已被她迷倒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 你一定要鼓起勇氣表白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也要去社團不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 宇佐的話一定會答應你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因為宇佐她是個好女孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:11.42,BackGround,,0,0,0,,總之加油吧 內卷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:14.12,BackGround,,0,0,0,,不好意思 今天突然把妳叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:17.15,BackGround,,0,0,0,,別放在心上 這是緊急事件嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:19.33,BackGround,,0,0,0,,可是伊萬莉同學妳還在掛病號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,文化祭的空罐藝術在市民美術節上獲得銀獎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只要努力不懈 就一定會有收穫的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學姑且不論
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還得向小山老師報告一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 剛才那話什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,只要努力不懈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,今天社長怎麼不先來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 叫那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,只有宇佐美同學先來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我有話要對妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是很嚴肅的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要冷靜下來聽他說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？ 內卷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以馬上給他回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要讓他著急…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他困惑…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要掌握主動權
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,主導權…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:54.70,BackGround,,0,0,0,,好的 我也喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.45,BackGround,,0,0,0,,蹦～♡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.19,BackGround,,0,0,0,,蹦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你說她？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 你不是說她的兔子髮飾很可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:13.67,BackGround,,0,0,0,,兔兔♡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個 很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,生氣時會變得有點野蠻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯 就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:21.08,BackGround,,0,0,0,,教訓一下～♡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到妳還挺瞭解的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,裙底不時會走光…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,原來妳知道這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,請妳看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:26.91,BackGround,,0,0,0,,心跳不已～♡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這個第一集的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他當時在看的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:36.99,BackGround,,0,0,0,,蹦～♡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙嗎！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢 可以說句好久沒說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,請說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不就畫嗎！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,終究是人畫殊途 你難道不這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為愛是可以跨越次元的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,說的話倒是很帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不對不對 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候肯定有提到我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:14:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,妳指什麼事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…我聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你和伊萬莉的談話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你說…喜歡上我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是說了「喜歡宇佐美同學」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 看來是我的說明不夠充分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,其實她的名字叫作兔美啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:21.09,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※與「宇佐美（うさみ）」同音。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\1c&HE6DBDD&\fs30\pos(538,6)}擁有十二生肖的兔屬之力的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.08,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H575F63&\fs40\pos(612,58)}兔美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,虧我還認真聽你說那麼多廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不說這個 我有事拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,被兔美同學的可愛徹底征服的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可愛！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我指這位兔美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太容易混淆了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,對 就是很容易混淆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣？ 是想叫我改名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我會提那麼沒良心的要求？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是難以啟齒罷了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真毒舌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我換個稱呼就解決了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,換什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞希同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,以後能叫妳瑞希同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因為 你講的太突然了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 今天只是想向妳告知這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那請妳考慮考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,唉～唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,妳打算怎麼回覆他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,社、社長！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候在那裡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,妳鬼鬼祟祟進社辦的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是一開始就在嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是很好嗎 「瑞希同學」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你們實在沒什麼進展
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明年我就不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你們能待在社辦的日子也會變少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再不抓緊的話 時間可會一瞬即逝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:11.93,BackGround,,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:16.08,BackGround,,0,0,0,,那個時間帶去買的話會比較便宜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.31,BackGround,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:21.60,BackGround,,0,0,0,,偶爾還會在那裡碰巧遇上鄰居呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞希
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 沒食慾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
