Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:01.63,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\bord0\1c&H457C85&\fs35\pos(492,186)}香織
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:01.63,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\\b0\bord0\fs30\1c&H555757&\pos(514,252)}哦～那不是很好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:01.63,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\b0\bord0\fs35\1c&H1A3C53&\pos(570,370)}嗯～～～……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:01.63,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\b0\bord0\fs30\1c&H1A3C53&\pos(570,400)}可是我又還沒做好心理準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:01.63,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\b0\bord0\fs30\1c&H1A3C53&\pos(572,580)}今天已經很晚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,妳居然就這樣保留回答嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:13.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs35\1c&HE0E1EB&\pos(575,90)}涼沙瑞加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,小嫩嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:13.04,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H457C85&\fs30\pos(480,190)}沙耶加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:13.04,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H457C85&\fs30\pos(496,326)}香織
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:13.04,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H457C85&\fs30\pos(496,452)}涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可是可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,被喜歡的男生直呼名字不是好事一樁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有點混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只是無法接受理由對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,心動！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎 哇—真難搞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,戀愛中的少女就是難搞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs35\1c&HE0E1EB&\pos(559,30)}涼沙瑞加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,本日最中肯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H457C85&\fs30\pos(472,154)}香織
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H457C85&\fs30\pos(454,316)}沙耶加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:43.90,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H457C85&\fs30\pos(472,476)}涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很難搞的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:23.52,BackGround,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒這麼好天氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天讓我考慮的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我的答覆是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,NO 拒絕 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不會這麼輕易就讓你稱心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是稱呼妳宇佐美同學比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這跟你昨天說的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說和喜歡的角色名字一樣會混淆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:21:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,別再聊那隻狐狸精的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:04.40,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\bord0\shad4\1c&H624FB9&\4c&H2B0E15&\pos(910,40)}鬱卒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天播放了動畫第五集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,讓人驚嘆的作畫 可愛的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是讓人覺得溫馨的前半段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是到了後半段我才發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那隻狐狸精竟然有男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,明明都有我了 這完全是出軌了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學大概不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡的人已經死會的這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼一來你也明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,愛是無法跨越次元…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,說得沒錯 老婆果然還是要自己親手來畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好 今天也要努力畫老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的老婆就畫制服裝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.87,BackGround,,0,0,0,,可以請妳再當一次模特兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 隨他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:21:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,想請妳擺出這個姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行 做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學的話 我也能夠勉強忍受的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是勉強嗎！
Comment: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF
